criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Scheduled for elective arthroscopic RCR;

          -  First time RCR on the target shoulder;

          -  Completed primary and secondary outcome measures (Western Ontario Rotator Cuff Index
             (WORC), Constant Score, Maximum Pain on Numeric Rating Scale and EQ-5D-5L) from daily
             routine.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Changes of intra operative procedure (e.g. anything but RCR)

          -  Re-repair of tendon;

          -  No surgery;

          -  Other pain-related or neurological comorbidities that could interfere with pain
             measures;
